{"tid":2421472,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"自家製紅燒乳鴿","createTime":"2021-02-24T13:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T10:57:12.000Z","uid":239860,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ba09b404c41dfba1f3fb7e98dfa805ec0fc85827","tid":2421472,"uid":239860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:49:47.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇係大排檔叫過炸乳鴿食，我以前成日會叫隻乳鴿再加碗蠔仔粥一齊食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今次我就整左炸乳鴿，個做法都有少少繁複，浸下炸下咁，有興趣可以睇下條片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IMVEE5YNkls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIMVEE5YNkls&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8Cvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=38a4579f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IMVEE5YNkls</a><br />\n製成品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ESDO22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ESDO22.jpg&h=5f83be51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢兩隻乳鴿我係超市買, $78，都幾大隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZwX4BL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZwX4BL.jpg&h=108b181c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洗完乳鴿就浸落D滷水汁到，枝滷水汁我係超市買，但自己再買包滷水料掉埋落去一齊煮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0gJfJR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0gJfJR.jpg&h=4cef13a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先用細火煮20分鐘，再焗10分鐘  <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZoAubhj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZoAubhj.jpg&h=de30e419&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後隻乳鴿先浸一浸熱水，再煮埋個脆皮水<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1VJznpc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1VJznpc.jpg&h=6d38fc1e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n脆皮水淋係隻鴿上面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tbqenpq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftbqenpq.jpg&h=09c9766a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淋完之後攤凍左就可以拎去炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NgBEywk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNgBEywk.jpg&h=c444eace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n炸完出黎就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QdW5t4N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQdW5t4N.jpg&h=80461ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣就訂閱埋我個ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nig: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CGaAioqJrXL/?igshid=17jre4m7bfvma\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCGaAioqJrXL%2F%3Figshid%3D17jre4m7bfvma&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8Cvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=287e417a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCGaAioqJrXL%2F%3Figshid%3D17jre4m7bfvma&h=f5148637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CGaAioqJrXL/?igshid=17jre4m7bfvma</a>"},{"pid":"7bdcc581198d9a5a1f7078b958b3f524f07731d3","tid":2421472,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:51:17.000Z","msg":"樓主提供如何處理受傷野外雀仔素材<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07a42ddc353f7af4c5e2e80383e6ac8a1e54284","tid":2421472,"uid":52228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"係咪炸子雞都可以咁樣整<br />\n好正！"},{"pid":"3596b3a0fc8993ae5a738ea56118b61a987d59b2","tid":2421472,"uid":329977,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:52:28.000Z","msg":"連登介紹自己Channel係大忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10be82e8f12c3931b7e9c796e8046214985d6ad8","ti